Acked-by: Hou Tao <houtao1@huawei.com>
Acked-by: Shung-Hsi Yu <shung-hsi.yu@suse.com>
---
 kernel/bpf/hashtab.c |    2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

--- a/kernel/bpf/hashtab.c
+++ b/kernel/bpf/hashtab.c
